======================
The Blu Shell (BluSH)
======================

This shell currently offers functionality comparable to Squaak.

---------------
Building Blu
---------------

This project was built using Parrot v4.0.0. Before building Blu,
please ensure that Parrot is on your system and its executables
are located on your $PATH.

To build Blu, run:

cd src
parrot setup.pir

---------------
Running Blu
---------------

To execute a file written in Blu, run:

./installable_blu [filename.blu]

A number of example programs may be found in the sample_code directory.
